88c842e0fc950c84bf1dd184a53e2_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="连君曼"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/zhuangxiu/lian-jun-man-84/answers" class="answers text-muted">3 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/lian-jun-man-84" data-hovercard='p$t$lian-jun-man-84'>连君曼</a><div class="bio">鬼手帕 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 室内设计师</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/she-ji-shi-shi-kong" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$she-ji-shi-shi-kong'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-97398941ffb57397ab845c4d98483d1a_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="设计师石空"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/zhuangxiu/she-ji-shi-shi-kong/answers" class="answers text-muted">13 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/she-ji-shi-shi-kong" data-hovercard='p$t$she-ji-shi-shi-kong'>设计师石空</a><div class="bio">石空設計 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 设计总监</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/wang-zhi-feng-22" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-zhi-feng-22'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/ea5e01974_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="王志峰"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/zhuangxiu/wang-zhi-feng-22/answers" class="answers text-muted">24 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/wang-zhi-feng-22" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-zhi-feng-22'>王志峰</a><span class="icon icon-badge-best_answerer icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者"></span><div class="bio">北京蜜蜂兄弟科技有限公司 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> CEO</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/hei-suan-suan-28" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$hei-suan-suan-28'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-9db39cad5d74e31a9ce5f89b94dfa7b9_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="鲜橙汁儿"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/zhuangxiu/hei-suan-suan-28/answers" class="answers text-muted">12 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href=